         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">13th April [18]81 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you that the Trustees have re-considered your offer of the collection of German Scientific Works of Herr Fischer, and I am instructed to inform...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">81.04.13</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Robert Curtis</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No 24, p. 307, unit 1, VPRS 5887 Secretary's outward letter books p. 307, VA 912 Trustees of the Public Library, Museum and National Gallery of Victoria, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">13th April [18]81</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you that the Trustees have re-considered your offer of the collection of German Scientific Works of Herr Fischer, and I am instructed to inform you that they are prepared to accept the collection as per list for the sum of One hundred and twenty five pounds.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>marginal addition: '£125'. See H. Sheffield to M, 6 April 1881<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(in this edition as 81-04-06a), and the notes thereto. It would appear that M himself paid for both the Rothschild and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Theodor<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Fischer collections and was subsequently reimbursed by the Library, since at a meeting of the Library Committee on 28 June,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>his account for £175 was passed for payment; see State Library of Victoria, Trustees of the Public Library, Gallery and Museum, Minutes, vol. 13a (MSF12855).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Robt Curtis.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Secretary to the Trustees.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
